</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="84" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="21" pageNumber="84">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="21" pageNumber="84">
<bibRefCitation author="De la Rua, P" journalOrPublisher="Apidologie" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="699 - 708" title="Molecular characterization and population structure of Apismellifera from Madeira and the Azores." url="https://doi.org/10.1051/apido:2006044" volume="37" year="2006">
De la 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Rúa">Rua</normalizedToken>
et al. (2006)
</bibRefCitation>
analysed genetic diversity of Azorean honeybees and found a comparably low number of mitochondrial haplotypes, some of them shared with Madeiran honeybees, other probably recent introductions from the mainland.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
